Package: binance.com
Title: Binance Crypto Exchange Market Data Client for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the Binance/Binance.US public API.
    Current prices, 24h tickers, OHLCV klines (all intervals), order book
    depth, recent trades, exchange info. No auth for public data.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports: httr2, jsonlite, dplyr, tibble
